reviewText: The title speaks for itself!  It does get you up and moving.  I like the segments for each type of workout from adult to kids to seniors.  You really can do them all though and get a nice workout in.  Nice job!
This is a wonderful DVD. .. So blessed to have known this strong lady... This video is a product of her purpose.  I hope everyone gets to experience this ....

Outstanding fitness DVD!!! The moves were very easy to follow and to duplicate on my own. Definitely is a must have for people of all fitness levels. Sorena even encorporates children into a fun fitness routine. Lastly, you can't beat the price. I strongly encourage you to buy this DVD and/or recommend it to your friends.
